title: Super Smash Bros.™ Ultimate – Battling with Sora – Nintendo Switch
author: Nintendo
description:
The iconic Keyblade wielder arrives to the battlefield. 

Sora from KINGDOM HEARTS will be the final Super Smash Bros.™ Ultimate DLC fighter! Look forward to the release of Sora in Challenger Pack 11 on 10/18. 

Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/2021/sora-from-kingdom-hearts-revealed-as-the-final-dlc-fighter-coming-to-super-smash-bros-ultimate/

Download more Super Smash Bros.™ Ultimate DLC: https://smashbros.nintendo.com/buy/dlc/
